data.description: Presenting an immaculate 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence in Tampa, FL that harmoniously balances classic charm with modern comfort. This meticulously maintained home boasts spacious bedrooms exuding inviting warmth and natural light. While the bathrooms retain their original character, they showcase exceptional cleanliness and functionality. Ideal for those seeking a partially updated home, this property offers a timeless aesthetic that's been thoughtfully preserved. Experience the epitome of cleanliness and comfort in this well-preserved haven, where traditional elegance meets modern convenience.
